            <title><![CDATA[Switch 2 Preorders Open To Pure Chaos And More Of The Week's Top Stories]]></title>
            <link>https://kotaku.com/switch-2-preorders-oblivion-remaster-marvel-rivals-1851777869</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/switch-2-preorders-open-to-pure-chaos-and-more-of-the-weeks-top-stories.1174455/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://kotaku.com/switch-2-preorders-oblivion-remaster-marvel-rivals-1851777869<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><div><figure id="" data-id="10b8e682df5127ad00f7f5a8b6ccf77c" data-recommend-id="image://10b8e682df5127ad00f7f5a8b6ccf77c" data-format="jpg" data-width="1280" data-height="720" data-lightbox="false" data-recommended="false" data-hide="false" contenteditable="false" draggable="false"><div contenteditable="false" data-link-reference="" data-link-target="" data-syndicationrights="false" data-imagerights="in-house-art" data-hide="false" data-hidecredit="false"><p><figcaption>Image<!-- -->: <!-- -->Nintendo / Kotaku<!-- -->, <!-- -->Virtuous / Bethesda / Kotaku<!-- -->, <!-- -->Bethesda<!-- -->, <!-- -->Nintendo / eBay / Kotaku<!-- -->, <!-- -->Screenshot<!-- -->: <!-- -->Bethesda / Kotaku<!-- -->, <!-- -->Bethesda / Kotaku<!-- -->, <!-- -->Marvel / Kotaku</figcaption></p></div><span data-id="10b8e682df5127ad00f7f5a8b6ccf77c" data-recommend-id="image://10b8e682df5127ad00f7f5a8b6ccf77c" data-format="jpg" data-width="1280" data-height="720" data-lightbox="false" data-recommended="false" data-hide="false"></span></figure><div><p>This week saw a few massive happenings in the world of games. First and foremost, after being delayed to allow Nintendo to take stock of the potential impact of President Trump’s chaotic implementation of tariffs, the company finally kicked off retail pre-orders for the Switch 2 here in the U.S., and the results were chaotic. People struggling to place orders on sites like Walmart’s and Target’s encountered all kinds of errors, confusion, and sometimes even cancelation of orders they thought they’d successfully placed.</p><p>Elsewhere, Bethesda finally released <em>The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion Remastered </em>after years of rumors and speculation, and <em>Marvel Rivals </em>support players are going on strike. Read on for these stories and more.</p></div></div><div><figure id="" data-id="0da6a8b0b1d35158dba3a49b00a2bd2f" data-recommend-id="image://0da6a8b0b1d35158dba3a49b00a2bd2f" data-format="jpg" data-width="1920" data-height="1080" data-lightbox="false" data-alt="Mario is confused by Switch 2 preorder chaos. " data-recommended="false" data-hide="false" contenteditable="false" draggable="false"><div contenteditable="false" data-alt="Mario is confused by Switch 2 preorder chaos. " data-link-reference="" data-link-target="" data-syndicationrights="true" data-imagerights="other-license" data-hide="false" data-hidecredit="false"><p><figcaption>Image<!-- -->: <!-- -->Nintendo / Kotaku</figcaption></p></div><span data-id="0da6a8b0b1d35158dba3a49b00a2bd2f" data-recommend-id="image://0da6a8b0b1d35158dba3a49b00a2bd2f" data-format="jpg" data-width="1920" data-height="1080" data-lightbox="false" data-alt="Mario is confused by Switch 2 preorder chaos. " data-recommended="false" data-hide="false"></span></figure><p>Switch 2 preorders <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/switch-2-preorder-amazon-walmart-best-buy-gamestop-1851777336&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/switch-2-preorder-amazon-walmart-best-buy-gamestop-1851777336">went live online at 12:01 a.m. ET</a></span> and were every bit the mess some fans feared: pages timing out, error messages that weren’t real, and email cancelations being received just moments after it seemed like orders had gone through. There must be a better way to do these. Not in time for the Switch 2 launch, unfortunately. - Ethan Gach <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/switch-2-preorder-walmart-target-best-buy-nintendo-1851777604&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/switch-2-preorder-walmart-target-best-buy-nintendo-1851777604">Read More</a></span></p></div><div><figure id="" data-id="fd4c6c7b21737fc3586ae965abde6750" data-recommend-id="image://fd4c6c7b21737fc3586ae965abde6750" data-format="jpg" data-width="1920" data-height="1080" data-lightbox="false" data-recommended="false" data-hide="false" contenteditable="false" draggable="false"><div contenteditable="false" data-link-reference="" data-link-target="" data-syndicationrights="true" data-imagerights="fair-use" data-hide="false" data-hidecredit="false"><p><figcaption>Screenshot<!-- -->: <!-- -->Bethesda / Kotaku</figcaption></p></div><span data-id="fd4c6c7b21737fc3586ae965abde6750" data-recommend-id="image://fd4c6c7b21737fc3586ae965abde6750" data-format="jpg" data-width="1920" data-height="1080" data-lightbox="false" data-recommended="false" data-hide="false"></span></figure><p>After many reports, leaks, and rumors, Bethesda officially unveiled <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/bethesda-elder-scrolls-oblivion-remaster-stream-real-1851777087&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/bethesda-elder-scrolls-oblivion-remaster-stream-real-1851777087"><em>The</em> <em>Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion Remastered</em></a></span>. And the $50 remaster is launching today on Xbox Series X/S, Game Pass, PS5, and PC.  - Zack Zwiezen <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/bethesdas-oblivion-remaster-is-out-now-on-xbox-ps5-an-1851777265&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/bethesdas-oblivion-remaster-is-out-now-on-xbox-ps5-an-1851777265">Read More</a></span></p></div><div><figure id="" data-id="536448c3b93483d24bc90fbe4caf11e1" data-recommend-id="image://536448c3b93483d24bc90fbe4caf11e1" data-format="jpg" data-width="1920" data-height="1080" data-lightbox="false" data-alt="A Khajiit soldier wears chainmail." data-recommended="false" data-hide="false" contenteditable="false" draggable="false"><div contenteditable="false" data-alt="A Khajiit soldier wears chainmail." data-link-reference="" data-link-target="" data-syndicationrights="true" data-imagerights="fair-use" data-hide="false" data-hidecredit="false"><p><figcaption>Screenshot<!-- -->: <!-- -->Bethesda / Kotaku</figcaption></p></div><span data-id="536448c3b93483d24bc90fbe4caf11e1" data-recommend-id="image://536448c3b93483d24bc90fbe4caf11e1" data-format="jpg" data-width="1920" data-height="1080" data-lightbox="false" data-alt="A Khajiit soldier wears chainmail." data-recommended="false" data-hide="false"></span></figure><p>Though we’ve known it’s coming for a few days now, today Bethesda showed off its fancy new remaster of 2006's <em>The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion</em>, and it looks spectacular. It’s also <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/bethesdas-oblivion-remaster-is-out-now-on-xbox-ps5-an-1851777265&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/bethesdas-oblivion-remaster-is-out-now-on-xbox-ps5-an-1851777265">out, like, right-friggin-now</a></span>! If you want to check out the whole reveal, <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://youtu.be/kk5cymSWmqo&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://youtu.be/kk5cymSWmqo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">you can do so here</a></span>. But if you just want to peruse some lovely screenshots we nabbed during the reveal, read on.  - Claire Jackson <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/elder-scrolls-oblivion-remastered-screenshots-1851777292&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/elder-scrolls-oblivion-remastered-screenshots-1851777292">Read More</a></span></p></div><div><figure id="" data-id="1411743ec3decb7a6e31e026fb87f6fe" data-recommend-id="image://1411743ec3decb7a6e31e026fb87f6fe" data-format="jpg" data-width="1600" data-height="900" data-lightbox="false" data-alt="Luna Snow casts ice magic." data-recommended="false" data-hide="false" contenteditable="false" draggable="false"><div contenteditable="false" data-alt="Luna Snow casts ice magic." data-link-reference="" data-link-target="" data-syndicationrights="true" data-imagerights="fair-use" data-hide="false" data-hidecredit="false"><p><figcaption>Screenshot<!-- -->: <!-- -->Marvel / Kotaku</figcaption></p></div><span data-id="1411743ec3decb7a6e31e026fb87f6fe" data-recommend-id="image://1411743ec3decb7a6e31e026fb87f6fe" data-format="jpg" data-width="1600" data-height="900" data-lightbox="false" data-alt="Luna Snow casts ice magic." data-recommended="false" data-hide="false"></span></figure><p>Being a support player in a hero shooter is a thankless job. You keep everyone alive, and then your bad teammates still blame you when they run off and die trying to 1v6 the enemy team. Things have gotten so bad in the eyes of some <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/marvel-rivals-review-hero-shooter-overwatch-netease-1851717975&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/marvel-rivals-review-hero-shooter-overwatch-netease-1851717975"><em>Marvel Rivals</em>’</a></span> <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/marvel-rivals-strategist-supports-best-worst-luna-snow-1851738627&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/marvel-rivals-strategist-supports-best-worst-luna-snow-1851738627">Strategist</a></span> mains that a group of them are going on “strike” by refusing to play the role and instead queueing up to play as tank and damage heroes instead. - Kenneth Shepard <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/marvel-rivals-strategist-support-strike-tiktok-necros-1851777718&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/marvel-rivals-strategist-support-strike-tiktok-necros-1851777718">Read More</a></span></p></div><div><figure id="" data-id="744c10527b154ffdf4a6f0fd3438722b" data-recommend-id="image://744c10527b154ffdf4a6f0fd3438722b" data-format="jpg" data-width="1920" data-height="1080" data-lightbox="false" data-alt="A knight in steel armor stands in front of a demonic portal. " data-recommended="false" data-hide="false" contenteditable="false" draggable="false"><div contenteditable="false" data-alt="A knight in steel armor stands in front of a demonic portal. " data-link-reference="" data-link-target="" data-syndicationrights="true" data-imagerights="fair-use" data-hide="false" data-hidecredit="false"><p><figcaption>Leaked artwork of the Oblivion remaster. </figcaption><figcaption>Image<!-- -->: <!-- -->Virtuous / Bethesda / Kotaku</figcaption></p></div><span data-id="744c10527b154ffdf4a6f0fd3438722b" data-recommend-id="image://744c10527b154ffdf4a6f0fd3438722b" data-format="jpg" data-width="1920" data-height="1080" data-lightbox="false" data-alt="A knight in steel armor stands in front of a demonic portal. " data-recommended="false" data-hide="false"></span></figure></div><div><figure id="" data-id="7dee9f98e13c64286edf2107f90269c3" data-recommend-id="image://7dee9f98e13c64286edf2107f90269c3" data-format="jpg" data-width="1917" data-height="1080" data-lightbox="false" data-alt="A wizard holds his staff. " data-recommended="false" data-hide="false" contenteditable="false" draggable="false"><div contenteditable="false" data-alt="A wizard holds his staff. " data-link-reference="" data-link-target="" data-syndicationrights="true" data-imagerights="other-license" data-hide="false" data-hidecredit="false"><p><figcaption>Image<!-- -->: <!-- -->Bethesda</figcaption></p></div><span data-id="7dee9f98e13c64286edf2107f90269c3" data-recommend-id="image://7dee9f98e13c64286edf2107f90269c3" data-format="jpg" data-width="1917" data-height="1080" data-lightbox="false" data-alt="A wizard holds his staff. " data-recommended="false" data-hide="false"></span></figure><p>The worst-kept secret of the year, Bethesda’s current-gen remaster of <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/bethesdas-oblivion-remaster-is-out-now-on-xbox-ps5-an-1851777265&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/bethesdas-oblivion-remaster-is-out-now-on-xbox-ps5-an-1851777265"><em>The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion</em>, finally shadow-dropped</a></span> yesterday and the Xbox-360-era open-world RPG has wasted no time in reminding fans why it was such a hit nearly two decades ago. Complete with refreshed graphics, updated gameplay, and cherished memes intact,  <em>Oblivion Remastered </em>is already topping Steam charts and taking players on an Unreal Engine 5-made trip down memory lane.  - Ethan Gach <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/oblivion-remaster-elder-scrolls-eso-glitch-meme-1851777557&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/oblivion-remaster-elder-scrolls-eso-glitch-meme-1851777557">Read More</a></span></p></div><div><figure id="" data-id="e5d5ba47c521684bef44dcd02271fb95" data-recommend-id="image://e5d5ba47c521684bef44dcd02271fb95" data-format="png" data-width="1629" data-height="916" data-lightbox="false" data-alt="Mario jumps near a Switch 2. " data-recommended="false" data-hide="false" contenteditable="false" draggable="false"><span data-id="e5d5ba47c521684bef44dcd02271fb95" data-recommend-id="image://e5d5ba47c521684bef44dcd02271fb95" data-format="png" data-width="1629" data-height="916" data-lightbox="false" data-alt="Mario jumps near a Switch 2. " data-recommended="false" data-hide="false"></span></figure><p>Switch 2 preorders don’t begin in the U.S. until late tonight (<span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/switch-2-preorder-amazon-walmart-best-buy-gamestop-1851777336&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/switch-2-preorder-amazon-walmart-best-buy-gamestop-1851777336">12:01 a.m. ET on April 24</a></span>), but they’ve already been underway in other parts of the world and even Nintendo has been shocked by the level of demand so far. The company said that, with over 2.2 million fans seeking to preorder a Switch 2 directly from My Nintendo in Japan alone, the demand already “far exceeds” its ability to fulfill shipments to that country at launch. - Ethan Gach <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/switch-2-preorders-my-nintendo-japan-sold-out-1851777449&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/switch-2-preorders-my-nintendo-japan-sold-out-1851777449">Read More</a></span></p></div><div><figure id="" data-id="15794791b8215004fc89d9d1d1c76fca" data-recommend-id="image://15794791b8215004fc89d9d1d1c76fca" data-format="jpg" data-width="1920" data-height="1080" data-lightbox="false" data-recommended="false" data-hide="false" contenteditable="false" draggable="false"><div contenteditable="false" data-link-reference="" data-link-target="" data-syndicationrights="true" data-imagerights="fair-use" data-hide="false" data-hidecredit="false"><p><figcaption>Image<!-- -->: <!-- -->Nintendo / eBay / Kotaku</figcaption></p></div><span data-id="15794791b8215004fc89d9d1d1c76fca" data-recommend-id="image://15794791b8215004fc89d9d1d1c76fca" data-format="jpg" data-width="1920" data-height="1080" data-lightbox="false" data-recommended="false" data-hide="false"></span></figure><p>Just an hour after <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/switch-2-preorders-my-nintendo-japan-sold-out-1851777449&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/switch-2-preorders-my-nintendo-japan-sold-out-1851777449">Switch 2 pre-orders</a></span> went live on April 24 in the United States, <em>Kotaku </em>has spotted over two dozen eBay listings for the upcoming Nintendo console. Some are real. Others are actually people making fake listings to throw off bots and scalpers.  - Zack Zwiezen <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/switch-2-preorders-ebay-resellers-scalpers-nintendo-1851777605&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/switch-2-preorders-ebay-resellers-scalpers-nintendo-1851777605">Read More</a></span></p></div><div><div data-video-id="197541" data-monetizable="true" data-position="kinjavideo" data-video-title="Civilization VII’s Latest Update Finally Feels Like The Game Fans Were Promised" data-video-blog-id="9" data-video-network="kotaku" data-video-duration="147" data-playlist="197541" data-current="197541" id="197541"><div><p>Civilization VII’s Latest Update Finally Feels Like The Game Fans Were Promised</p></div><video disablepictureinpicture="" playsinline="" poster="https://no.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fill,h_542,pg_1,q_60,w_965/197xrjaz7466rpng.png" data-poster="https://no.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fill,h_542,pg_1,q_60,w_965/e71b6a16c12407233933bf5382f5d7a1.png" width="100%" height="100%" crossorigin="anonymous" preload="none"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/197541/197541_240p.mp4" label="240p" type="video/mp4"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/197541/197541_480p.mp4" label="480p" type="video/mp4"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/197541/197541_720p.mp4" label="720p" type="video/mp4"><track kind="captions" label="English" src="https://kinja.com/api/videoupload/caption/23067.vtt" srclang="en"></video><div><ul><li data-label="">Off</li><li data-label="English">English</li></ul></div></div><p>The 4X strategy sequel just got a ton more highly requested features</p></div><div><div data-video-id="197531" data-monetizable="true" data-position="kinjavideo" data-video-title="Disney's New Lo-Fi Goofy Video Is Hiding A Kingdom Hearts Tease" data-video-blog-id="9" data-video-network="kotaku" data-video-duration="152" data-playlist="197531" data-current="197531" id="197531"><div><p>Disney's New Lo-Fi Goofy Video Is Hiding A Kingdom Hearts Tease</p></div><video disablepictureinpicture="" playsinline="" poster="https://no.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fill,h_542,pg_1,q_60,w_965/197xrjaz7466rpng.png" data-poster="https://no.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fill,h_542,pg_1,q_60,w_965/f174887e6bbba7b5e0508c53e6afc6ad.jpg" width="100%" height="100%" crossorigin="anonymous" preload="none"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/197531/197531_240p.mp4" label="240p" type="video/mp4"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/197531/197531_480p.mp4" label="480p" type="video/mp4"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/197531/197531_720p.mp4" label="720p" type="video/mp4"><track kind="captions" label="English" src="https://kinja.com/api/videoupload/caption/23063.vtt" srclang="en"></video><div><ul><li data-label="">Off</li><li data-label="English">English</li></ul></div></div><p>It seems like Goofy’s son Max is a fan of his dad’s multiverse adventure</p></div></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
